data.description: SELLER'S ARE WILLING TO PAY $10,000 towards buyer's closing costs and pre-paids with acceptable offer! Fantastic, completely remodeled, shows-like-new waterfront piece of heaven, nestled away in a quiet, friendly riverfront neighborhood, minutes from all that downtown Fort Myers has to offer.  Partial list of features:    -generous 3/3 plus flex room split layout, with 2 en-suite baths, four homes from the Caloosahatchee River  -large open floor plan  -outstanding all-new chef's kitchen with top of the line appliances  -attached in-law or income apartment with private entry  -extra wide canal lot with plenty of room for boats and toys  -spacious outdoor entertainment area and canal-side patio with river views  -car collector / mechanic's dream garage - RV + 2 cars, 7000lb rotary lift, newer 80 gal compressor tank, 200 amp svc, fabulous garage storage rack system with 16' garage ceiling  -30 amp RV hookup and a triple-wide driveway  -newer A/C system, irrigation system and water heater  -new roof 2023  -fenced in yard for your pets or kids    You CAN have it all!
